**DDoS Protection – Included free of charge:**

Our KVM VPS are protected by the OVH anti-DDoS infrastructure in order to protect your IP Addresses and domain(s) 24/7 against any type of DDoS attack, regardless of duration or size. A DDoS attack aims to render a server, service or an infrastructure unavailable by sending a multitude of simultaneous requests from multiple points across the internet. The intensity of this “crossfire” renders the service unstable, or even worse, unavailable.

